@startuml
[*] --> ViewTime : user views time
ViewTime --> AdjustTime : user presses button to adjust time
AdjustTime --> IncreaseValues : user increases values while adjusting time settings
IncreaseValues --> AlarmFeature : user switches to alarm feature
AlarmFeature --> SetAlarmTime : user sets alarm time
SetAlarmTime --> TriggerAlarm : set alarm time matches current time
TriggerAlarm --> StopAlarm : user presses button to stop alarm
StopAlarm --> LightFeature : user presses button to turn on light
LightFeature --> TurnOffLight : user releases button to turn off light
@enduml
